RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.COLLATERAL_CODE, a.COLLATERAL_DESC FROM LBTMS_COLLATERAL a WHERE a.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND a.AUTH_STAT = 'A' and NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 from LBTM_TRANCHE_COLLENT_COLL where TRANCHE_REF_NO = ? and EFFECTIVE_DATE = ? and COLLATERAL_CODE = a.COLLATERAL_CODE)

SELECT E.ENTITY_CODE, E.ENTITY_DESC, E.ENTITY_TYPE FROM LBTMS_COLLATERAL_ENTITY E WHERE (E.ENTITY_TYPE = ? OR E.ENTITY_TYPE = 'CollateralEntity') AND E.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND E.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTMS_TRANCHE_COLLENT_ENTITY WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = ? AND EFFECTIVE_DATE = ? AND COLLATERAL_CODE = ? AND ENTITY_CODE = E.ENTITY_CODE)
